			description: [
				"§6The Minoshroom§f guards the center of the §eTwilight Labyrinth§f —"
				"§fa massive underground maze. Defeating it opens the §eHydra Lair§f."
				""
				"§eFinding the Labyrinth:§r"
				"§7• Large hedge-maze structure. Use §eMagic Map§7 after Lich defeat."
				"§7• §eMaze Map§7 (craftable) reveals the Labyrinth interior layout."
				""
				"§eNavigating the Labyrinth:§r"
				"§7• §eLight torches§7 as you go — the maze is enormous and dark."
				"§7• §eMaze Wafer§7 item (found in maze chests) gives Labyrinth map info."
				"§7• §eMinotaurs§7 patrol the halls — hostile, deal moderate damage."
				"§7• §eCentral chamber§7 has the Minoshroom — large mushroom-headed bull."
				""
				"§eFight:§r"
				"§7• §eMinoshroom§7 charges and stomps. High health, moderate damage."
				"§7• §eKeep moving§7 — charge attacks are telegraphed, easy to sidestep."
				"§7• §eArs Nouveau§7 Projectile + Harm + Pierce + Amplify hits from safe range."
				""
				"§eDrops:§r"
				"§7• §eMeef Stroganoff§7 — the most nutritious Farmer's Delight-adjacent meal"
				"§7  in the pack. Grants Strength I for 30 seconds when eaten."
				"§7• §eTrophy§7 (Minoshroom Head) — for the trophy room."
				""
				"§a► Defeat the Minoshroom and collect Meef Stroganoff. Mark done."
			]
