			title: "The Hydra — Boss 4/6"
			icon: "twilightforest:hydra_trophy"
			description: [
				"§6The Hydra§f is the most visually impressive Twilight boss — a"
				"§fmulti-headed fire-breathing serpent in a §eFire Swamp§f lair."
				"§fDefeating it unlocks the §eDark Tower§f (Ur-Ghast)."
				""
				"§eFinding the Hydra Lair:§r"
				"§7• Large circular burned clearing in the §eFire Swamp§7 biome."
				"§7• §eFireflies§7 from Alex's Mobs mark the swamp edge at night."
				""
				"§eFight strategy:§r"
				"§7• §eMultiple heads§7 — each fires fire breath or lunges to bite."
				"§7• §eShoot open mouths§7 with arrows/spells when heads rear back to fire."
				"§7  Open mouth = vulnerable for ~1 second. That's your window."
				"§7• §eDo not use fire§7 — the Hydra is immune. Projectile + Harm + Amplify."
				"§7• §eSever a head§7 — it regrows as two. Only destroy heads when you can"
				"§7  kill two replacements — or §enever sever§7 heads and just whittle health."
				"§7• §ePotion of Fire Resistance§7 — mandatory. The swamp floor is on fire."
				""
				"§eDrops:§r"
				"§7• §eHydra Trophy§7 — Ch 7.3 display."
				"§7• §eFiery Blood§7 (reward) — required for Fiery Ingot crafting (next quest)."
				""
				"§a► Defeat the Hydra and collect the Trophy."
			]
			dependencies: ["00120004"]
		}

