				""
				"§eFinding the Dark Tower:§r"
				"§7• An enormous black tower visible from far away in §eDarkwood§7 biome."
				"§7• Multiple floors of Carminite-powered traps and Ghast spawners."
				"§7• §eClimb carefully§7 — each floor has new trap mechanics."
				""
				"§eDark Tower interior:§r"
				"§7• §eCarminite Golem§7 rooms — large constructs, high HP."
				"§7• §eGhastling§7 spawners — mini-ghasts that deal significant damage."
				"§7• §eCarminite Traps§7 — explode when stepped on. §eDeactivate with redstone§7."
				"§7• §eRooftop§7 — where the Ur-Ghast spawns."
				""
				"§eFight strategy:§r"
				"§7• §eReflect§7 Ur-Ghast fireballs back with a §esword swing§7 (like vanilla Ghast)."
				"§7• §eOr use a Bow§7 — Power V bow deals massive damage to its large hitbox."
				"§7• §eArs Nouveau§7 Projectile + Harm + Amplify → 15+ damage per cast."
				""
				"§eDrops:§r"
