			icon: "twilightforest:snow_queen_trophy"
			subtitle: "The final boss of the Twilight Forest"
			description: [
				"§6The Snow Queen§f rules the §eAurora Palace§f — a towering ice cathedral"
				"§fat the heart of the §eGlacier§f biome. She is the final Twilight Forest boss."
				""
				"§eFinding the Aurora Palace:§r"
				"§7• §eGlacier biome§7 — white ice fields and towering aurora spires."
				"§7• The Palace is the largest structure in the Glacier. Hard to miss."
				"§7• §eNavigate§7 through ice rooms and Penguin mob chambers to reach her throne."
				""
				"§eFight strategy:§r"
				"§7• §eSnow Queen§7 hovers and fires ice bolts, ice bombs, and frost rays."
				"§7• §eIce bombs§7 freeze you in place — §ebreak free§7 by swinging rapidly."
				"§7• §eFrost ray§7 deals sustained cold damage — §edodge sideways§7."
				"§7• §eHigh mobility§7 wins this fight. §eElytra§7 (Ch 3.5) is excellent here."
				"§7• §eArs Nouveau§7 Projectile + Harm + Amplify + Burst works well."
				"§7• §eFire damage§7 does bonus damage — §eFire Aspect§7 sword or §eIgnite glyph§7."
				""
				"§eDrops:§r"
				"§7• §eSnow Queen Trophy§7 — Ch 7.3 display. §eThis completes all 6.§7"
				"§7• §eIce Bombs§7 — throw to freeze mobs on contact. Excellent utility."
